			<div class="post-1308 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-personal-privacy tag-build-privacy-fence tag-chain-link-fencing tag-culture tag-diy tag-fence-contractors tag-fences tag-fencing-material tag-fourth-amendment tag-hedge tag-identity tag-mandy-moore tag-michael-moore tag-philosophy tag-plain-view-doctrine tag-police-searches tag-privacy tag-privacy-fence-slats tag-privacy-fences tag-privacy-fencing tag-privacy-hedge-benefits-hedges tag-privacy-hedges tag-vinyl-fence tag-vinyl-privacy-fence tag-wood-fences tag-wood-privacy-fence tag-wood-privacy-fences post_box top" id="post-1308">
