<p>This article indicates that vinyl is less expensive than wood, but from what I&#8217;ve found elsewhere, including cost range estimates you can get if you enter the fencing amount in linear feet using Homewyse&#8217;s fence installation cost calculator, vinyl appears to be MORE expensive than wood.  This confuses me a bit.</p>
</div>
					</dd>
				</dl>
